":"웨일스 글램르건 랜데위","lifeSummary":"Alice Welsh(이)가 1254년 영국 웨일스 글램르건 랜데위에서 태어났을 때, 그녀의 아버지 Sir John Welsh(은)는 29세였고, 그녀의 어머니 Mrs. John Welsh(은)는 25세였다. 그녀는 1270년 영국 웨일스 글램르건에서 Carodoc Ap Leuan 8th Lord of Cardigan(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 한 명의 아들과 두 명의 딸을 두었다. 그녀는 영국 웨일스에서 사망했다."},"lv":{"1254–":"1254. gads–mirusi","1240–Female":"1240–mirusi","1254–Female":"1254.gads–mirusi","1250–1290":"1250–1290","1250–Male":"1250–miris","1273–Male":"1273.gads–miris","1275–Female":"1275–mirusi","1304–Female":"1304.gads–mirusi","1225–1280":"1225–1280","1229–Female":"1229–mirusi","1304":"1304. gads","1225":"1225","1254":"1254. gads","Abt 1275":"ap 1275. gadu","1275":"1275","1273":"1273. gads","1240":"1240","1250":"1250","1270":"1270. gads","1280":"1280","1229":"1229","1290":"1290","Coity, Glamorgan, Wales":"Coity, Glamorgan, Velsa, Lielbritānija","Llanddewi, Glamorganshire, Wales":"Llanddewi, Glamorgan, Velsa, Lielbritānija","Wales":"Velsa, Lielbritānija","of Miscin,,, Wales":"Velsa, Lielbritānija","Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Velsa, Lielbritānija","Llanddewi, Glamorgan, Wales":"Llanddewi, Glamorgan, Wales"},"mg":{"1254–":"1254–Maty","1240–Female":"1240–Maty","1254–Female":"1254–Maty","1250–1290":"1250–1290","1250–Male":"1250–Maty","1273–Male":"1273–Maty","1275–Female":"1275–Maty","1304–Female":"1304–Maty","1225–1280":"1225–1280","1229–Female":"1229–Maty","1304":"1304","1225":"1225","1254":"1254","Abt 1275":"tany ho any amin'ny 1275","1275":"1275","1273":"1273","1240":"1240","1250":"1250","1270":"1270","1280":"1280","1229":"1229","1290":"1290","Coity, Glamorgan, Wales":"Coity, Glamorgan, Pays de Galles, United Kingdom","Llanddewi, Glamorganshire, Wales":"Llanddewi, Glamorgan, Pays de Galles, United Kingdom","Wales":"Pays de Galles, United Kingdom","of Miscin,,, Wales":"Pays de Galles, United Kingdom","Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Pays de Galles, United Kingdom","Llanddewi, Glamorgan, Wales":"Llanddewi, Glamorgan, Wales"},"ms":{"1254–":"1254–Mati","1240–Female":"1240–Mati","1254–Female":"125